Description: Screen Lock Application for Interactive Boards
 ASKilit is a screen lock application designed for interactive
 educational boards. It prevents students from using the board
 without teacher authorization.
 .
 Features:
  - EBA QR code login for teachers
  - Offline QR code login fallback
  - Automatic screen lock after inactivity
  - Touch detection for activity monitoring
